              "id": "ph_q6",
              "type": "MCQ",
              "latex": true,
              "question": "The equation of a wave is $y = A\\sin(kx - \\omega t)$. The speed of the wave is:",
              "options": [
                "$\\frac{k}{\\omega}$",
                "$\\frac{\\omega}{k}$",
                "$k\\omega$",
                "$\\frac{1}{k\\omega}$"
              ],
              "answer": [1],
              "explanation": "Wave speed $v = \\frac{\\omega}{k} = f\\lambda$."
            }
          ]
